front.title: •Baniss Keeg, Pilot Instructor
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power and 1 to hyperspeed of anything she pilots. Once per turn, if you just deployed a Black Sun agent to same system, may draw top card of Reserve Deck. Your characters here are immune to Cantina Brawl and Fallen Portal.
front.lore: Duros information broker, scout, and smuggler.
